# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy to .env.local for local dev; add the same vars in Vercel → Settings →
# Environment Variables (Production + Preview). Server-side only, never committed.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# PRIMARY DATA (required for full stock analysis incl. DCF) ----------------
# Financial Modeling Prep — free 250/day. https://site.financialmodelingprep.com
FMP_API_KEY=

# NARRATIVE (set one; optional) --------------------------------------------
# Google Gemini — FREE, no card. https://aistudio.google.com/   (recommended)
GEMINI_API_KEY=
# GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-2.0-flash
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=        # paid alternative

# BACKUP DATA SOURCES (optional, free — used when FMP is exhausted) ---------
# Finnhub — free, 60/min, no daily cap. Powers peers + quote fallback.
#   https://finnhub.io/
FINNHUB_API_KEY=
# Alpha Vantage — free, 25/day. Fundamentals/quote backup AND the source for
# the fund/ETF view (holdings + expense ratio via ETF_PROFILE).
#   https://www.alphavantage.co/support/#api-key
ALPHAVANTAGE_API_KEY=
# (Stooq is used for price history — free, keyless, no env var needed.)

# MENTION HISTORY + REDDIT POSTS (optional) --------------------------------
# Upstash Redis (Vercel Marketplace) auto-injects KV_REST_API_URL / _TOKEN.
CRON_SECRET=
# REDDIT_CLIENT_ID=
# REDDIT_CLIENT_SECRET=
